<p>
  Your team's canvases are available for export in the form of a series of
  <strong>Markdown files</strong> (one per canvas). The export can take a few
  minutes so we'll email you when your export is ready for download.
</p>

<div>
  <button local-class="export-button {{if isExporting 'disabled'}}" {{action (toggle 'isExporting' this)}}>
    {{#if isExporting}}
      Exporting...
    {{else}}
      Start Export
    {{/if}}
  </button>

  {{#if isExporting}}
    <span local-class="confirmation">
      <strong>Export started!</strong> We will email you a download link as soon
      as it is done.
    </span>
  {{/if}}
</div>

